<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white p-3 md:p-6"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <!-- Problema In pasticceria -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
      <div class="flex-1 p-4 bg-custom-blue-light rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-3">In pasticceria</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-800 mb-2">In pasticceria il papà di Barbara ordina il dolce al cioccolato per 2 bambini e il dolce alla frutta per 4 bambini.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-800 font-bold">Quanto spenderà il papà di Barbara?</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start justify-center">
        <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p072/output-1715938802072_603_310_392_196.png", alt: "Listino prezzi pasticceria", class: "w-[392px] h-[196px]" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Domande -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
        <span class="text-gray-700">– Il testo contiene tutte le informazioni per risolvere il problema?</span>
        <div class="inline-flex border border-gray-400 rounded overflow-hidden">
          <label class="px-3 py-1 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100 border-r border-gray-400"><input type="radio" name="pasticceria1" value="si" class="mr-1">Sì</label>
          <label class="px-3 py-1 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100"><input type="radio" name="pasticceria1" value="no" data-correct-answer="true" class="mr-1">No</label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
        <span class="text-gray-700">– Quali informazioni mancano?</span>
        <input type="text" class="flex-1 max-w-md px-2 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent focus:outline-none" data-correct-answer="i prezzi dei dolci">
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
        <span class="text-gray-700">– L'immagine contiene le informazioni che mancano nel testo?</span>
        <div class="inline-flex border border-gray-400 rounded overflow-hidden">
          <label class="px-3 py-1 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100 border-r border-gray-400"><input type="radio" name="pasticceria2" value="si" data-correct-answer="true" class="mr-1">Sì</label>
          <label class="px-3 py-1 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100"><input type="radio" name="pasticceria2" value="no" class="mr-1">No</label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <span class="font-bold text-gray-700">Risposta:</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700">Il papà di Barbara spenderà</span>
        <input type="text" class="w-20 px-2 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent text-center focus:outline-none" data-correct-answer="34">
        <span class="text-gray-700">euro.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Problema grafico spese -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700">• Sul grafico è rappresentato l'andamento delle spese della famiglia Bianchi dell'anno scorso.</p>

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700">– In quale mese la famiglia Bianchi ha speso di più?</span>
            <input type="text" class="w-32 px-2 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent focus:outline-none" data-correct-answer="agosto">
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700">– In quale ha speso di meno?</span>
            <input type="text" class="w-32 px-2 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent focus:outline-none" data-correct-answer="febbraio">
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700">– Quanti euro ha speso in un anno intero?</span>
            <input type="text" class="w-32 px-2 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent focus:outline-none" data-correct-answer="16200">
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700">– A metà anno era già stata spesa la metà della spesa annuale?</span>
            <div class="inline-flex border border-gray-400 rounded overflow-hidden">
              <label class="px-3 py-1 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100 border-r border-gray-400"><input type="radio" name="spese1" value="si" class="mr-1">Sì</label>
              <label class="px-3 py-1 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100"><input type="radio" name="spese1" value="no" data-correct-answer="true" class="mr-1">No</label>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-gray-700">– Secondo te, perché la famiglia ha speso di più ad agosto e a dicembre?</span>
            <input type="text" class="w-full mt-1 px-2 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent focus:outline-none">
          </div>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p072/p072_01.jpg", alt: "Grafico spese famiglia", class: "w-[300px] h-[214px]" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Problema parallelogramma -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700">• Il disegno rappresenta il cortile di una scuola: calcola l'area.</p>

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-3">
          <div>
            <span class="text-gray-700">– Come si calcola l'area del parallelogramma?</span>
            <input type="text" class="w-full mt-1 px-2 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent focus:outline-none" data-correct-answer="base x altezza">
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">– Osservando il disegno puoi trovare le misure necessarie:</p>
            <div class="space-y-2 ml-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="text-gray-700">misura della base del parallelogramma:</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent text-center focus:outline-none" data-correct-answer="20">
                <span class="text-gray-700">m</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="text-gray-700">misura dell'altezza del parallelogramma:</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent text-center focus:outline-none" data-correct-answer="15">
                <span class="text-gray-700">m</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="text-gray-700">misura dell'area del parallelogramma:</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-12 px-1 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent text-center focus:outline-none" data-correct-answer="20">
                <span class="text-gray-700">m ×</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-12 px-1 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent text-center focus:outline-none" data-correct-answer="15">
                <span class="text-gray-700">m =</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-12 px-1 py-1 border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 bg-transparent text-center focus:outline-none" data-correct-answer="300">
                <span class="text-gray-700">m²</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p072/p072_02.jpg", alt: "Parallelogramma cortile", class: "w-[350px] h-[160px]" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
